                },
                "bulk": {
                    "type": "stat_block_section",
                    "subtype": "bulk",
                    "value": null,
                    "text": "L"
                },
                "text": "As moderate, but the tail can hold an item of up to 1 Bulk or be used as a second hand to help hold an item of up to 2 Bulk. You can also use the limb to make an unarmed attack that deals 1d6 bludgeoning damage and has the sweep trait. This potion lasts 24 hours.",
